    "title": "『信じる』",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『菊花賞』後――学校やトレーニングに出ず、\n無気力な日々を過ごすナリタタイシンは\nあるバスケットボールの試合を見て驚く。",
            "enText": "After the Kikka-sho, NARITA Taishin, \nwho has been lethargic, not attending \nschool or training, is surprised to \nsee a basketball game.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "pathId": -8325453976221429801,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "テレビの中で活躍するのは『皐月賞』前、\nナリタタイシンに厳しい言葉を\n投げかけてきた小さな赤髪の少女だった。",
            "enText": "The little red-haired girl who had \nspoken harsh words to Narita Taishin \nbefore \"Satsuki-sho\" was the one \nwho was active on TV.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 268,
                    "pathId": 1165970888753696630
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -4666500821838390546
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": -692124267809927513
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": 4947240830399208311
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3360633635002287955,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ひねくれているが誰よりも強く、\n絶対に諦めない誰かから\n『諦めない勇気』をもらったという少女。",
            "enText": "A girl who is twisted, but stronger than \nanyone else, and who says she got the \n\"courage to never give up\" from someone who \nnever gives up.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 268,
                    "pathId": 1649300522228984028
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": 5048078901588100115
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": 7677398184840719335
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -7094703106915187337
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4497590977701610511,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "逆境に負けぬ強さを持つナリタタイシンに\n励まされ、奮い立たせられてきたと話す\nウイニングチケット。",
            "enText": "Winning Ticket says she has been encouraged \nand inspired by Narita Taishin's strength in \nthe face of adversity.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 268,
                    "pathId": 377170034790686156
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -2661188953801052467
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": 4211868266685764323
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -3134645121839384074
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8716658432836786009,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そして、ナリタタイシンを信じ、\n復帰を毎日待ち続けたトレーナーからの\n真摯な励ましを受け――",
            "enText": "And with the sincere encouragement of her \ntrainer, who believed in Narita Taishin and \nwaited every day for her return…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 208,
                    "pathId": 8299359997254759257
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 429,
                    "pathId": 5542934561471530443
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": 5616589374718046373
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": 6935610143847240487
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4352328815201510322,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "諦めたくないという気持ちを取り戻した\r\nナリタタイシンは、\n『日経賞』でのリベンジを決心するのだった。",
            "enText": "Narita Taishin regained her determination not \nto give up, and decided to take revenge in \nthe Nikkei Award.",
